"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**CT Markets Pro User: I only know of a few other platforms that build off of BTC to maximize its security, decentralization, and popularity (Lightning, RSK, Sovryn). So why do you think there aren’t more protocols integrating with BTC?**\\n\\n**MC:** It’s the difficulty of it. It took core engineers and the Blockstack team a while to crack Proof of Transfer, making the fully expressive contract layer possible in a truly decentralized way. When you have the option of working with a restrictive and unmoving base like Bitcoin or something else (or creating your chain entirely), I think many will end up in that last bucket. It’s an easier path and with how hot crypto is, is I can assume it’s more immediately lucrative, so that’s where the focus has stayed.\",\"timestamp\":1639127207,\"title\":\"of Scientific and Technological Innovation between Russia and\"},\"digest\":\"LuMI_FQNpn8qXo1XBEPe3BsdDbchu3bP_FaY6RtDCO8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9eB6C10b208F81a8e370434A1E29071B354a4331\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RNvc4zqOIqA-DkuezeHfGsxfI70ufb7WDKH_em9sDUg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fSVc2N8kP6L0vKjGvg51VB8lV1vZSG96cDOU4sFFHh8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"YXRDL6oU0IVrdVZBOgDIBD-u8hZ5ajBDVa3zU1k1f6b918QMPQkt0Ex0BvQb7G1tfAVBa5SnHiUmZpfx4aGzzQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x275942d048186d7c9b32edbffa6902c77f554698f98c53e5dca124b97bd0f5493d732272e4c82d1ff5b5a5c625a59653bac83af4bfd61fb41d329b0f06b6685d1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"RNvc4zqOIqA-DkuezeHfGsxfI70ufb7WDKH_em9sDUg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fSVc2N8kP6L0vKjGvg51VB8lV1vZSG96cDOU4sFFHh8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"LuMI_FQNpn8qXo1XBEPe3BsdDbch